        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center pt-8">
            <a
                href="#about"
                class="px-8 py-3 bg-white text-black font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors"
            >
                About Me
            </a>
            <a
                href="/mozi-rig"
                class="px-8 py-3 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors"
